Àtụ:MedalTableTop
Emem Edem (amuru 15 October 1983) bu onye oso Naijiria larala ezumike nka bu onye puru iche na 100 mita
Ọ gbachara nke ise na 100 mita na 1999 World Youth Championship, ma zọọkwa na 200 mita n'ebe ahụ
Na mpaghara nke obodo ọ gbahara nke isii na 100 mita wee nweta ihe nrite ọla edo na 4 × 100 mita relay n'egwuregwu All-Africa nke afọ 2003.
